The Chairman of the National Union of Road Transport Workers in Lagos State, Musiliu Akinsanya, aka MC Oluomo, has endorsed Mike Edward, one of the finalists in the Big brother Naija 2019 reality show. Mike’s wife, met with the NURTW boss during her visit to Nigeria. Akinsanya, in a video shared on social media expressed his support for the BBNaija housemate with the contestant’s wife, Perri Shakes-Drayton, standing all smiles beside him. The NURTW boss was seen holding a T-shirt on which Edward’s face was emblazoned, He said “Please, vote for Mike. My people everywhere, I beg you in the name of God. You know the reason I like Mike is that he sang about me.” https://www.instagram.com/p/B3KdAHXAqHY/?utm_source=ig_embed&utm_campaign=dlfix